Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They learned about the ruler of the island\N---Caesar Clown's motive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all while trying to escape Shinokuni,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with their pirate ally \N- the Warlord - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others are on \Nthe move to kidnap Caesar,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save the children, and \Nescape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have that crazy pirate backing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Seven Warlords \N- Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:04:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I broke... the gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Caesar's Defeat!-- The \NPowerful Grizzly Magnum!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deadly gas - Shinokuni will fill \Nup the building-- in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors are all heading \Ntoward R Building -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "R-66" door, the only \Nexit to escape. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:56.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,B BUILDING - SANJI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling lifted up just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gas has started flowing \Nin from the cracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everybody! Get to R Building now!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time for wimping out, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain-chan!\N--I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you beat that bird woman, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are they coming from that direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were behind \Nus to let us get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The G-5 is coming this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we were going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, p-put me down! \NThis is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pain! Just stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:06:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who said you can carry \NTashigi-chan on your shoulder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry up, everybody!\N--This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Broke the gear"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no turning back"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:09.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,B BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - THE EXAMINATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling's gonna collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper-yan, it's not safe to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I've done all I could for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to R Building now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, count on us! Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha! Stay with me! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will I eat breakfast tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know you're going to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know Joker's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstarts like you who have \Nacquired just a touch of fame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't hope to take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's filled with those \Nwho are much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him, Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you squirts got is energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world is much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just worry about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Vergo the pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:16.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,R BUILDING 1ST FLOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something is falling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who could have done such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Vergo doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Some of us buried under the wreckage!\N--Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You assholes ruined my "paradise"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if everybody is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta take advantage of this confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Now let's look for \Nthe Sea Prism Stone handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Straw Hat member's gone!\N--Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R Building 2nd floor, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Master is okay, \Nwe're gonna be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret room, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the air vents now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Shinokuni flow into this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a gas man. I'm not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get our fellow soldiers \Non the 1st floor upstairs first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Now"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Do it now"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are over a hundred soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are just a bunch of guinea pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would care if \Nhundreds of you die or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the dregs of society!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can find replacements \Nfor you fools so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinokuni is my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they know who Caesar really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I control the doors \Nfrom here, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why're you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is trying to fool the enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have a plan about \Nthe deadly gas, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna let his people die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is a kind man. It would hurt him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he finds out we suspected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! I opened the air vents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! The deadly gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flowing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You should've done \Nas I said from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dregs shouldn't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, become my power! Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LAND OF DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my scientific power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:15:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kicking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Straw Hat Luffy! \NThis amazing appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my scientific power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through this experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,two countries have already expressed \Ninterest in the weapon - Shinokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both quite peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when humans get serious \Nabout defending themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll look for any way \Npossible to kill their enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spread weapons all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become the king of the \Nland of death (Shinokuni)!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He killed our fellow soldiers!\N--What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he really think of us as guinea pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how fast it works on their nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost an art!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, look after Brownbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going, Straw Hat Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you chicken out all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But B Building beyond that path is \Nalmost filled up with Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no place to run \Non the island anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for all of you guinea pigs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who the Master really is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trusted him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. I know you're broken-hearted \Nbut could I sit in that control seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna save my friends from the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching it, weren't you? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I know you all watched it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. We've \Nbeen terribly betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we know that he was our enemy but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't run from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But so are you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just see your \Ncaptain run from Caesar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took off leaving you guys behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa, are you dissing our \Ncaptain right in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were the kind of \Nperson who would betray us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would've been easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've just run away with \Nmy tail between my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he never ever stops...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...believing in us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we had no choice but to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We pledged to live up to his \Nexpectations as long as we breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are just crumbs. You \Nshouldn't stand against your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drop dead like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What should we do?\N--There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't beat such a powerful man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, you can!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should just believe in our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the type of person that \NLuffy hates the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your savior and I can make efficient \Nuse of you good-for-nothings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy won't forgive Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever wanna see your face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your death is going to be the \Nclimax of this experiment show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Grizzly Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, drop dead! Behold my scientific power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kneel before my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.10,0:22:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can work under me if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has crushed Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shocking news...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...spreads across the New \NWorld in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an assassin sent by Doflamingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...flies toward the island of Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storm of a new battle rages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Raid! An Assassin from Dressrosa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
